item.title: Delete this
item.dc:creator: @ReaperXScape ReaperXScape
item.description:
@ReaperXScape wrote:

well i havent updated this in a while, so heres the lastest updates (there are more, here are the biggest ones though)

----now you can select xp rate ONLY THE FIRST TIME YOU EVER LOG IN, choosing expert will soon give a reward (for each different xprate you unlock a title.----

—Bank pins now save, and when you click the bank it asks you to “set a pin” “change your pin” “delete your pin” or “enter pin”
enter pin will just allow you to access the bank----

— the unused sidebar is now a minigame teleports tab—

— added items on death, they do not completely work yet, (i coded it, but used the same interface as futurescape, because i didnt find any other interfaces that would’ve worked—

—new part to quest tab, it sais some important info and achievements—

— dice bag, allows you to host (dropped by bosses) another way of hosting is flower game—

— quest now save “progress” on the quest you are doing (red = not started, yellow = in progress, green = done)----

—working kill/death ratio (you may wonder, why i have this because its an allstar and you can pretty much 1 shot kill players, but i had an idea to make it so that you get less maxhit in a wildy area, just to make pking equal)—

— some of the yell titles, just to show off lol, i will add make 40+ i plan on having around 50 total all with different requirements—
